      "q1": "How do I register a new check-in?",
      "a1": "To register a new check-in, navigate to the \"Check-In\" section in the sidebar and complete the form with the guest's information. All marked fields are mandatory. Once completed, click on \"Register Check-In\" to finish the process.",
      "q2": "How do I search for a registered guest?",
      "a2": "You can search for guests in two ways: 1) In the \"Check-In\" section, select the \"Registered Guests\" tab and use the search box. 2) Go directly to the \"Guests\" section in the sidebar and use the search box to filter by name, email, or ID number.",
      "q3": "How can I modify data from a completed check-in?",
      "a3": "To modify a check-in, navigate to the \"Check-In\" section, select the \"Registered Guests\" tab, find the record you want to modify and click on the edit icon (pencil). Make the necessary changes and save.",
      "q4": "How do I change the system configuration?",
      "a4": "Access the \"Settings\" section in the sidebar. There you can modify the hotel information, default schedules, notification settings, and other system settings. Remember to save the changes when you're done.",
      "q5": "Can I export guest data?",
      "a5": "This functionality will be available in future updates. For now, you can view all records in the \"Guests\" section."
